The wife of the Sun Correspondent in Cross River State, Mrs Uduak Judex Okoro has been kidnapped. Mrs Okoro was kidnapped on Tuesday by 8.30pm around Big Qua town in Calabar Municipal local government area of the state The husband, Mr Judex Okoro who is the Chairman of the Correspondent’s Chapel confirmed the ugly incident in Calabar. He said this is one incident too many, noting that the wife had earlier been kidnapped seven years ago, “All relevant security operatives have been informed” he stated.